title: Super Junior’s Shindong To Join SISTAR’s Soyou And More For “Law Of The Jungle”
text:
Shares 182   
Super Junior’s Shindong is the latest cast addition to the SBS variety show “ Law of the Jungle ” in New Zealand! 
On March 18, a source from the variety show stated that Shindong will be joining Lee Kyung Kyu , SISTAR’s Soyou , Apink’s Jung Eun Ji , and After School’s Uee , who have already been confirmed to appear on the show. 
Meanwhile, “Law of the Jungle” in New Zealand will start to air at the end of March. 
Are you excited for the upcoming cast and location of “Law of the Jungle”?
